values:
Well i knew it would happen and it did so why do i hurt so bad?? I hurt so bad cuz i did like him a whole lot and he meant a lot to me.. And the thought of him bein with another gurl just kills me inside!! I guess they are all right it easier to dump someone than to be dumped!!

Lisa is the bestest friend ever! I dunno what i would do without her through all of this!! I love her to death and she means everything to me.. She is a true friend!!
Peace Easy

Well i havent had the best weekend at all. In fact it was horrible!! i found out that my dad is dying and that is very hard to deal with and then hank almost broke up with me.. That was the hardest of all. He means so much to me and i dont want to lose him ever. He is the best and means so much to me. Just one day with him makes everything better!! He is the most kind hearted caring person i know besides lis and i thank him for that!!

Lis is the best through all this. She is there for me through all of this and she listens and is more like a sister to me than anything else! I dunno what i would do with out her!!

Everythings goin good!! I went to Kohls though and spent more money than i should have lol!! Its so worth it though!! 
I GOT AN A- ON MY PRE CALC TEST!

Arica came in and saw me last night!! I love her to death!! I dont know where i would be with out her!! She is tryin to get me a job so i can work with her!! I cant stand wendys and i cant stand not talkin to her as much as what i used!! She really is my guardian angel!! I would do anything for that gurl!!

To all the hater call 1-800-lick-em and the website is www.lick-em.com!!
Much love
me

I am so sick of all the people here who run there mouths but wont do anything bout it!! It just pisses me off!

Well me and arica talked last night! I love her to death she is my guardian angel watching over me!! She is the best!!

Everything is good here!! I am so happy and nothin will ever change that!! I cant wait only a  year left till i graduate and move to west laffayette for college!! Cuz Im goin to purdue!! Then i get to be with  Brian all the time!! screw all the haters i know that brian is the one for me!! I know it ;)!! Well im out!

Today was better than what i thought it would be! I didnt have to put with some of the bitching today so that was good! I wish i could talk to brian though!! I dunno what to do bout brad! He read that stupid note after i told him not too. uhh.. so i dunno what to do now or say to him. or even how to act round him!! Then my other dilemma is what to do bout friday night! I will keep you posted on that one and tell you more bout it later!! well i got nothing now! Bye!

I am so happy!! Nothing can go wrong now!! Me and Brian are talkin and he is the best thing in the world!! I dunno what i would do with out him!! He has brought me so much happiness and i cant wait till i move up there when i go to college! Then I will be with him all of the time!! 

Some people at school are real bitches and i dont care what they think bout me!! Cuz their opinion doesnt matter!!

*I wanna be the gurl he sees and he smiles as he turns to his friends and says thats her!!*

You know what suck is when you really like someone and you have no idea if there can ever like you back again! Then you see them walk down the hall and you smile at them and they smile back and you just wanna melt but you may never ever have them back again!! That sucks big balls!

I am so sick of the backstabbers at school who will talk bad bout them and then wanna go do something with them! That makes me so mad!! And what is up with francesca lately? she is completely ignorin me and i dont understand why! Did i do something wrong? Oh well she dont want to be friends with me screw her!!She lost a good friendship and for what nothin!

The stupidest thing in the world is when every school around you has a 2 hour delay and maybe even closed and you have to go to school on time! Honestly how gay is that>

Everything is goin good here!! Goin to bobbi's house sunday for a big party for the super bowl! :) Went to kirstins today she kills me! Honestly who runs into walls! I have the bestest friends in the world! Then jess comes back to school tomorrow! =) I have missed her so much!! i dunno where i would be without her!! We have had our rough times but things are really lookin up for us now! Welp im out peace!

I hate being sick!! We finally get a snow day and i am sick!! Kirstin is the bestest friend that anyone could ever have! She gives the best advice and has always been there for me!! I would prolly die with out her!!LOL 
Me and arick talked today and i would do anything for him! I realized today how much of a big brother he was to me!! 
Other than that everythings good sides the usual backstabing b**ch at school and that just makes me mad!!  Well i think that im gonna go call kirstin or take a nice relaxing bath to help me feel better! Peace
